What is backened development? in SE
Backened engineers are the person who are responsible for maintaining code structure and system design.
Backened engineers are the person who are responsible for documenting the whole new feature.
Backened engineers are the person who are responsible for writing business logic.
Backened engineers are the person who are responsible for taking design decisions.

